{"tid":674323,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"歐聯皇馬派錢波,上樓好機會","createTime":"2018-05-22T14:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T20:42:05.000Z","uid":58346,"like":56,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"3674a3e7c1235961d2253344f1d52b9da64f8e62","tid":674323,"uid":58346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:51:21.000Z","msg":"皇家馬德里(主隊勝)     <del>和</del>\t利物浦(客隊勝)<br />\n          2.00\t            <del>3.65</del>\t         2.95<br />\n基於杯賽決賽唔會和呢個道理,和波呢項野可以唔撚洗睇 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n皇馬作為史上首支歐冠改制後連霸既球隊嬴波居然有2倍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再睇番狗會今年開皇馬嬴波初盤有2倍或以上既比賽既對手,分別係:<br />\n<del>維拉利爾</del> (季尾風流波,留力歐冠,可以唔撚洗睇) <br />\n巴塞       4戰2勝1和1負<br />\n拜仁       1戰1勝<br />\n祖雲       1戰1勝<br />\n巴黎      2戰2勝<br />\n馬體會  1戰1和<br />\n多蒙特  1戰1勝<br />\n以上除咗巴塞同馬體會 有3場嬴唔到之外,其餘都係全勝既<br />\n而拎利物浦同巴塞,馬體會呢2隊比,簡直係侮辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n皇馬6次入決賽6次都拎杯,100%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外,近3次皇馬拎歐冠,巴塞都係8強就出撚咗局(13-14,15-16,16-17) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇番利物浦,連反應可以快到捉到子彃既神龍米奴列都雪埋,用埋個連國家隊都未踢過既卡xxx<br />\n咁就連1%嬴既機會冇埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗起用懦夫雲守c朗,都扯扯地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我朗又可以準備入番3,5,7球刷下數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而懦夫雲又會比人屌撚到關ig  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後講多次皇馬嬴波係100%既事,買得多嬴得多<br />\n我就準備連腎都賣埋訓身皇馬了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/3c9tb9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3c9tb9c.jpg&h=3935bfad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85fb8b4ce7fd442625b7caed9998ff46d9987689","tid":674323,"uid":38683,"like":3,"dislike":23,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:53:29.000Z","msg":"點解唔會和波？<br />\n踢加時咪和波囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f907bb1f529ef3a6236cdf52627980223bb149","tid":674323,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:01:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">若要生活好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"906e13845894610e22207b8907aca4dbd6e8dcd2","tid":674323,"uid":58022,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:06:31.000Z","msg":"睇左第一段已經唔洗睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e56b31fd0edff7d9b5ec10491f560256762e46e","tid":674323,"uid":16343,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:08:18.000Z","msg":"傻鳩你賭過波未架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af06a6eec4830ce968cfba613038b285c55ac9e","tid":674323,"uid":35547,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:11:35.000Z","msg":"講咁多都係想燈姐"},{"pid":"b49f678bf66b6cd91426af31